# ── Frontend environment variables (Vite) ────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to `.env.production` for a prod build, or set these in the Cloudflare
# Pages dashboard (Settings → Environment variables). Only vars prefixed with
# VITE_ are exposed to the browser bundle.

# Base origin of the Django backend API.
#   - Dev: LEAVE UNSET / EMPTY. Relative /api/* paths go through the Vite proxy
#     (see vite.config.ts → server.proxy).
#   - Prod (Cloudflare Pages): set to the deployed backend origin, no trailing slash.
# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.temudosen.com
